scopecontent.head: Scope and Contents
scopecontent.p: Collection primarily contains ten years of Inteleads, Intel Corporation's employee newsletter. This 1979-1989 run from vol.3 no.6 through vol.13 no.5 is missing only a handful of issues, and includes annual April Fool's editions and other extras. The collection also includes other magazines, promotional booklets, recruitment brochures, users manuals, technical specifications, etc. Intel is a corporation and technology company headquartered in Santa Clara, California that was founded by Gordon Moore and Robert Noyce.
